{{Databox|en=Abdallah ibn Azzuz}}
'''Ɛbdllah ibn Ɛazzuz''' ittyussan s wassaɣ n Sidi Balla, immut g usggas n 1789. iga yan umara amɣribi, ar bahra ittara f ttaṣawwuf, macc ar ittara ula f [[tasnijjit]]. iwra tugt n idlisn g igr n tasnijjit nɣ nzzḍar anini iwra f twwuriwin n usujji s yat tɣarast taqqbuṛt. iwra ula f usujji s imɣyan.

